#: src/Module.php:142
msgid "A pedigree chart of an individual’s ancestors."
msgstr "Rodovnik prednikov osebe."

#: src/Configuration.php:414
msgid "Abbreviate given names first"
msgstr "Najprej skrajšaj osebna imena"

#: src/Configuration.php:415
msgid "Abbreviate surnames first"
msgstr "Najprej skrajšaj priimke"

#: src/Facade/DataFacade.php:202
msgid "Add a father"
msgstr ""

#: src/Facade/DataFacade.php:203
msgid "Add a mother"
msgstr ""

#: src/Configuration.php:413
msgid "Automatic (based on tree's surname tradition)"
msgstr "Samodejno (glede na drevesno tradicijo priimkov)"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/behavior.phtml:23
msgid "Behavior"
msgstr "Vedenje"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:23
msgid "Colors"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Colors the person boxes by family branch. Each couple shares the same color, "
"derived from the chosen base colors."
msgstr ""
"Obarva okvirje oseb glede na družinsko vejo. Vsak par si deli isto barvo, "
"izpeljano iz izbranih osnovnih barv."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:25
msgid "Control panel"
msgstr "Nadzorna plošča"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:97
msgid ""
"Controls which name part shrinks first when a box is too narrow for the full "
"name. \"Automatic\" uses the tree's surname tradition (Icelandic abbreviates "
"surnames; everything else abbreviates given names)."
msgstr ""
"Določa, kateri del imena se najprej skrajša, ko je polje preozko za polno "
"ime. »Samodejno« uporablja drevesno tradicijo priimkov (islandska tradicija "
"krajša priimke; vse ostale krajšajo osebna imena)."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:23
msgid "Details"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Displays a person's alternate name, if available. This simultaneously "
"enlarges the individuals' respective boxes to create the necessary space for "
"the display."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže nadomestno ime osebe, če je na voljo. Hkrati poveča ustrezna polja "
"oseb, da ustvari potreben prostor za prikaz."

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/png-export-button.phtml:18
msgid "Export as PNG"
msgstr "Izvozi kot PNG"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/svg-export-button.phtml:18
msgid "Export as SVG"
msgstr "Izvozi kot SVG"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:50
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/generations.phtml:22
msgid "Generations"
msgstr "Generacije"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/page.phtml:77
msgid "Hide more options"
msgstr "Skrij več možnosti"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:64
msgid "Hide the PNG export button"
msgstr "Skrij gumb PNG izvoz"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:55
msgid "Hide the SVG export button"
msgstr "Skrij gumb SVG izvoz"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/page.phtml:39
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "Oseba"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:46
msgid ""
"Inserts the GEDCOM NICK value in quotes between the given names and the "
"surname (e.g. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Mirrors the legacy webtrees "
"behaviour for trees that store nicknames in the separate GEDCOM NICK field."
msgstr ""
"Vstavi vrednost GEDCOM NICK v narekovajih med osebna imena in priimek (npr. "
"Martin \"Chalky\" White). Posnema staro vedenje webtrees za drevesa, ki "
"vzdevke shranjujejo v ločenem polju GEDCOM NICK."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:43
msgid "Maternal"
msgstr "Materina"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:25
msgid "Modules"
msgstr "Moduli"

#: src/Module.php:272
msgid "Move the view with two fingers"
msgstr "Premakni pogled z dvema prstoma"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:86
msgid "Name abbreviation when space is tight"
msgstr "Krajšanje imena, ko je prostor omejen"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/behavior.phtml:28
msgid "Open individual in new browser window/tab"
msgstr "Odpri osebo v novem oknu/zavihku brskalnika"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/behavior.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Open the current individual's detail page in a new browser window/tab when "
"it's left-clicked, otherwise the current window/tab is used."
msgstr ""
"Odpri stran s podrobnostmi trenutne osebe v novem oknu/zavihku brskalnika ob "
"kliku z levo tipko miške, sicer uporabi trenutno okno/zavihek."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/orientation.phtml:22
msgid "Orientation"
msgstr "Usmerjenost"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:39
msgid "Paternal"
msgstr "Očetova"

#: src/Module.php:131 src/Module.php:252
msgid "Pedigree chart"
msgstr "Rodovnik"

#: src/Module.php:249 src/Traits/ModuleChartTrait.php:43
#, php-format
msgid "Pedigree chart of %s"
msgstr "Rodovnik osebe %s"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/center-button.phtml:18
msgid "Re center"
msgstr "Znova na sredino"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:74
msgid "Show \"add parent\" placeholders for missing ancestors"
msgstr "Prikaži označevalce »dodaj starša« za manjkajoče prednike"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:28
msgid "Show alternative name of individual"
msgstr "Prikaži nadomestno ime osebe"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:28
msgid "Show family colors"
msgstr "Prikaži družinske barve"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/help-button.phtml:17
msgid "Show help"
msgstr "Prikaži pomoč"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/page.phtml:76
msgid "Show more options"
msgstr "Prikaži več možnosti"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:40
msgid "Show nicknames in display names"
msgstr "Prikaži vzdevke v prikaznih imenih"

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/fullscreen-button.phtml:18
msgid "Switch between full screen mode and normal view"
msgstr "Preklopi med celozaslonskim in običajnim načinom"

#: src/Traits/ModuleConfigTrait.php:111
#, php-format
msgid "The preferences for the module “%s” have been updated."
msgstr "Nastavitve modula “%s” so posodobljene."

#: src/Module.php:271
msgid "Use Ctrl + scroll to zoom in the view"
msgstr "Uporabi Ctrl+Scroll kolesce za povečavo diagrama"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:80
msgid ""
"When enabled, an empty box with a \"+\" icon is rendered in place of each "
"missing father or mother. Editors can click it to jump straight to the "
"webtrees \"add a parent\" form for the corresponding child. The placeholders "
"are only shown to users who have edit rights on the individual."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vklopljeno, se namesto vsakega manjkajočega očeta ali matere prikaže "
"prazno polje z ikono »+«. Urejevalci lahko nanj kliknejo, da skočijo "
"neposredno na obrazec webtrees »dodaj starša« za ustreznega otroka. "
"Označevalci so vidni samo uporabnikom s pravicami urejanja osebe."

